elements.name: TC_UI_SAL_16 - Verify dropdown updates after sales (if multiple tabs/windows)
elements.description:
"""
    Test Summary: Verify dropdown updates after sales (if multiple tabs/windows).
    Test Description: Test if plant stock updates in dropdown after a sale is made in another tab or window.
    Precondition: Admin logged in, Two browser tabs open with Sell Plant form, Plant "Mango Tree" has initial stock of 10.
    """

steps.name: user is logged into the application
user navigates to Sales List page
user is on Sales List page
Sell Plant button is visible
user clicks Sell Plant button
Sell Plant form should load successfully
plant "Mango Tree" is available in dropdown
Mango Tree has initial stock of 10
user opens new tab and navigates to Sell Plant form
user switches to Tab1
user selects "Mango Tree" from plant dropdown
user enters "3" in Quantity field
user clicks Sell button
sale should be successful
user navigates back to Sell Plant form

result.error_message:

steps.name: stock for "Mango Tree" should be 7 in Tab1
user switches to Tab2
user refreshes the page
page should refresh without errors
plant "Mango Tree" should be available in dropdown after refresh
stock for "Mango Tree" should be 7 in Tab2
